  "text": "Let me make an analogy that I have just thought of. A seven-stringed musical instrument may be played by deflecting each string, full deflection and releasing it, and getting a note. Or once the strings are capable of being deflected through their full deflection, producing a note, instead of producing the notes this way, taking the individual creative personality and deflecting each the proper amount in the proper sequence to produce the music. Is this correct? I am raising correct in the balanced individual, the energies lie waiting for the hand of the creator to pluck harmony.",
